<a id="date" style="display:none">2015-08-02</a><h1 style="clear: both;">Otuam SHS to be named after late Atta Mills</h1>
<div class="option-bar">
<p><a rel="nofollow" href="artikel.php?ID=372521&nav=previous">&laquo; Prev</a></p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="artikel.php?ID=372521&nav=next">Next &raquo;</a></p><p class="last"><a href="artikel.php?ID=372521&comment=0#com" rel="nofollow">Comments (19)</a></p>
